00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:42,360
So,

291
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,160
put it on for me.

292
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:04,040
How does it look?

293
00:15:05,680 --> 00:15:06,480
Does it suit me?

294
00:15:09,400 --> 00:15:10,920
[Why did the candle suddenly go out?]

295
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:15,000
[Is it...]

296
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:17,800
It looks good, quite good.

297
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:18,800
It's getting late.

298
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:19,880
I really should head back.

299
00:15:22,760 --> 00:15:23,560
So long!

300
00:16:10,560 --> 00:16:11,480
It's so late,

301
00:16:11,840 --> 00:16:13,440
Are you planning to keep watch for me?

302
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,000
Why are you still dawdling?

303
00:16:27,520 --> 00:16:28,640
Come over and sleep.

304
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:37,280
[Forget it,]

305
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:38,320
[it's not like]

306
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:40,080
[we haven't slept in the same bed before.]

307
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:41,360
[If I catch a cold,]

308
00:16:41,520 --> 00:16:42,960
[that would be self-inflicted suffering.]

309
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:53,720
Is that Pan Chi

310
00:16:54,520 --> 00:16:56,040
really your type?

311
00:16:56,800 --> 00:16:58,200
What do you mean by that?

312
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,280
Like conducting investigations?

313
00:17:02,680 --> 00:17:04,440
I do have quite a good rapport with him.

314
00:17:04,720 --> 00:17:05,160
Hey!

315
00:17:08,720 --> 00:17:09,880
What are you doing?

316
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:10,920
If you keep this up,

317
00:17:11,040 --> 00:17:12,120
I will go all out!

318
00:17:12,120 --> 00:17:13,160
Going all out?

319
00:17:14,840 --> 00:17:16,040
I'm curious to see

320
00:17:16,280 --> 00:17:18,040
what that is like?

321
00:17:31,560 --> 00:17:32,520
Shen Du,

322
00:17:33,959 --> 00:17:35,840
why are you awake at this late hour,

323
00:17:36,360 --> 00:17:37,479
acting all crazy?

324
00:17:51,480 --> 00:17:52,920
Someone's beating the drum to seek justice.

325
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:57,520
Who was beating the drum at the gate,

326
00:17:57,560 --> 00:17:58,680
and what grievance does he have?

327
00:17:59,280 --> 00:18:00,360
In response to my lord,

328
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:02,640
my name is Du Fusheng,

329
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:04,600
a merchant of herbal medicine.

330
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:05,640
Today is

331
00:18:05,640 --> 00:18:07,800
the wedding day of my youngest daughter,

332
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:09,880
Du Xiaowan and Li Hongfa's son,

333
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:11,040
Li Zimo.

334
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:13,720
Unexpectedly, a strange incident occurred.

335
00:18:14,080 --> 00:18:14,800
My daughter

336
00:18:14,800 --> 00:18:16,480
was present when she was welcomed in,

337
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:17,600
but after the wedding banquet, when they

338
00:18:17,600 --> 00:18:19,560
were about to share the nuptial cup,

339
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:22,000
she suddenly went missing.

340
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:23,240
[The incident happened so abruptly.]

341
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:24,880
[Despite our search, she remained missing.]

342
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:26,960
[So we came to report to the authorities.]

343
00:18:28,800 --> 00:18:30,560
On a joyous occasion with many guests,

344
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:31,800
this will be challenging to investigate.

345
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:33,200
Do you have a guest list?

346
00:18:33,800 --> 00:18:34,600
Yes, yes,

347
00:18:35,040 --> 00:18:35,840
it's right here.

348
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:37,800
Bring it up.

349
00:18:43,520 --> 00:18:44,720
Was the marriage between your two families

350
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:45,840
based on mutual consent?

351
00:18:46,520 --> 00:18:47,320
Yes, my lord,

352
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:50,240
Xiaowan and I are well-matched,

353
00:18:50,240 --> 00:18:51,200
and we cherish each other.

354
00:18:52,120 --> 00:18:53,800
[This outcome took everyone by surprise.]

355
00:18:54,760 --> 00:18:56,000
[I implore you, my lord,]

356
00:18:56,320 --> 00:18:57,520
to find Xiaowan for me.

357
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,000
Dispatch teams

358
00:19:02,280 --> 00:19:03,600
to both families for investigation.

359
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:04,680
Focus particularly on the Li family;

360
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:06,080
they require a meticulous examination.

361
00:19:06,280 --> 00:19:07,080
Look for any

362
00:19:07,080 --> 00:19:08,040
evidence that may have been overlooked.

363
00:19:08,440 --> 00:19:09,480
Pay special attention to

364
00:19:09,560 --> 00:19:10,920
the entries and exits of all doors.

365
00:19:11,040 --> 00:19:11,840
Understood!

366
00:19:17,600 --> 00:19:18,400
Lord Mo,

367
00:19:18,520 --> 00:19:20,160
the guest list's been thoroughly checked,

368
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:21,360
most guests are still present,

369
00:19:21,360 --> 00:19:22,600
with only a few unaccounted for.

370
00:19:23,240 --> 00:19:24,040
Locate them!

371
00:19:24,360 --> 00:19:26,040
Bring everyone back once found.

372
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:27,000
Yes!

373
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:30,480
What is it?

374
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:31,440
My lord,

375
00:19:31,560 --> 00:19:33,040
if we all go out to search,

376
00:19:33,040 --> 00:19:34,360
there may not be enough personnel

377
00:19:34,360 --> 00:19:35,280
to investigate the scene.

378
00:19:37,240 --> 00:19:38,040
Lord Mo,

379
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:39,960
if you lack manpower,

380
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,280
my guardsmen can assist.

381
00:19:46,040 --> 00:19:47,880
Then I'll count on you, Lord Shen.

382
00:19:56,680 --> 00:19:57,480
Jing Lin.

383
00:19:58,640 --> 00:19:59,440
My lord.

384
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:03,040
Proceed.

385
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:04,240
Yes!

386
00:20:05,280 --> 00:20:06,080
You all follow me.

387
00:20:06,560 --> 00:20:07,480
You all come with me as well.

388
00:20:44,800 --> 00:20:46,440
[Li Hongfa's family is affluent.]

389
00:20:47,160 --> 00:20:47,920
[The wedding house must be]

390
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:49,400
[meticulously decorated.]

391
00:20:50,520 --> 00:20:51,400
[There are no signs of]

392
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:52,520
[a struggle inside.]

393
00:20:58,680 --> 00:21:00,560
It appears that something occurred in here.

394
00:21:01,560 --> 00:21:02,560
In a fit of rage,

395
00:21:02,760 --> 00:21:04,040
someone damaged this.

396
00:21:07,360 --> 00:21:08,720
This is supposed to be a celebration,

397
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:10,880
yet everything here feels off.

398
00:21:12,080 --> 00:21:12,920
Furthermore,

399
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:14,080
just looking at this door frame,

400
00:21:14,080 --> 00:21:15,160
it's clearly been refurbished,

401
00:21:15,440 --> 00:21:17,160
yet there are signs of peeling paint.

402
00:21:18,120 --> 00:21:19,120
This definitely indicates a problem.

403
00:21:19,800 --> 00:21:21,080
I share your thoughts on this.

404
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:22,520
By the way,

405
00:21:22,600 --> 00:21:24,080
have you made any discoveries?

406
00:21:24,080 --> 00:21:25,120
I passed through the living room,

407
00:21:25,760 --> 00:21:27,240
and also went by the corner arbor

408
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:28,440
and the rockery,

409
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:30,000
but along the way,

410
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:31,880
I found nothing of note.

411
00:21:33,280 --> 00:21:34,320
That makes sense.

412
00:21:37,760 --> 00:21:39,240
The bride didn't leave of her own accord;

413
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:41,080
she was abducted by someone she knew,

414
00:21:41,080 --> 00:21:42,360
taken out through the back window.

415
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:55,600
With such a pressing case at hand,

416
00:21:56,840 --> 00:21:57,720
are you two still in the mood

417
00:21:57,720 --> 00:21:58,680
to chat idly here?

418
00:22:04,040 --> 00:22:05,880
I'm analyzing the case with Lady Yan.

419
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:07,680
How is that mere idle chatter?

420
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:09,080
Besides,

421
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:11,000
we've already reached a conclusion.

422
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:13,200
The bride

423
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:16,240
was indeed taken through this back window.

424
00:22:16,600 --> 00:22:17,400
Alright.

425
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:19,480
Time for certain individuals to get to work.

426
00:22:19,760 --> 00:22:21,800
Hurry and issue orders to search for her.

427
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:28,760
Very well,

428
00:22:29,520 --> 00:22:30,840
Mr. Pan, please lead the way.

429
00:22:31,600 --> 00:22:32,800
Along with my guardsmen

430
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:34,280
to pursue the suspects.

431
00:22:40,840 --> 00:22:42,400
Why did you leave in the middle?

432
00:22:42,800 --> 00:22:44,160
A servant of mine reported

433
00:22:44,280 --> 00:22:45,360
that my child fell sick,

434
00:22:45,560 --> 00:22:46,640
and my husband

435
00:22:46,720 --> 00:22:48,280
is unable to care for the child.

436
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:52,200
It was already quite late.

437
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:53,000
I couldn't

438
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:54,760
keep this up until dawn, right?

439
00:22:55,080 --> 00:22:56,040
My lord,

440
00:22:56,120 --> 00:22:57,120
please,

441
00:22:57,120 --> 00:22:57,840
don't mention this

442
00:22:57,840 --> 00:22:59,240
to my wife.

443
00:22:59,800 --> 00:23:00,680
I came here with the purpose

444
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:02,120
of checking on my mistress as well.

445
00:23:03,280 --> 00:23:04,520
At the wedding,

446
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:06,120
did anything

447
00:23:06,640 --> 00:23:07,680
unusual occur?

448
00:23:07,720 --> 00:23:08,600
Nothing at all.

449
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:11,280
Except for that...

450
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:14,240
Xu Jize performed quite well.

451
00:23:14,840 --> 00:23:16,000
I didn't notice anything else

452
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:17,160
out of the ordinary.

453
00:23:18,560 --> 00:23:19,680
As for Xu Jize,

454
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:21,200
he certainly had a tough time.

455
00:23:21,320 --> 00:23:22,520
Being a wedding attendant

456
00:23:22,560 --> 00:23:23,920
is not an easy task.

457
00:23:23,960 --> 00:23:25,720
There are very few in Yingzhou.

458
00:23:26,120 --> 00:23:27,280
But I heard that

459
00:23:27,600 --> 00:23:30,120
he has no recommendation.

460
00:23:30,120 --> 00:23:31,280
He had no way to secure a public position,

461
00:23:31,360 --> 00:23:33,080
so he became an wedding attendant.

462
00:23:37,360 --> 00:23:38,280
Let's go, everyone.

463
00:23:40,320 --> 00:23:41,480
Where's Xu Jize?

464
00:23:41,600 --> 00:23:42,560
Why isn't he here?

465
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:44,960
My lord,

466
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:45,800
he hasn't been located.

467
00:23:45,880 --> 00:23:46,800
You didn't find him?

468
00:23:48,120 --> 00:23:49,280
In that case,

469
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:50,360
[Xu Jize]

470
00:23:50,360 --> 00:23:52,160
[is the only one who left early]

471
00:23:52,760 --> 00:23:53,600
[and had the opportunity]

472
00:23:53,600 --> 00:23:54,920
[to get close to the bride.]

473
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:56,600
Lady Yan,

474
00:23:57,120 --> 00:23:58,000
do you think

475
00:23:58,400 --> 00:24:00,280
the culprit could be Xu Jize?

476
00:24:00,560 --> 00:24:02,040
At this moment, I can't provide an answer

477
00:24:02,040 --> 00:24:02,880
to that question.

478
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:05,080
Before the case is resolved,

479
00:24:05,360 --> 00:24:06,800
everyone present

480
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:08,040
is a suspect.

481
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:10,600
His absence from the scene

482
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:11,800
only suggests that

483
00:24:11,840 --> 00:24:13,480
his suspicion is even more pronounced.

484
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:15,600
At the end of the day,

485
00:24:15,600 --> 00:24:17,440
we still need evidence and witnesses.

486
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:24,840
You are Lord Commander's wife indeed.

487
00:24:25,280 --> 00:24:26,200
Though at a young age,

488
00:24:26,480 --> 00:24:28,280
you speak and act with great precision,

489
00:24:28,400 --> 00:24:29,920
and have your own set of principles.

490
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:32,480
From what you just said,

491
00:24:32,520 --> 00:24:34,040
it's clear you know

492
00:24:34,040 --> 00:24:34,840
my husband well.

493
00:24:37,560 --> 00:24:39,360
Detain them in the governor's office.

494
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:40,440
My lord!

495
00:24:41,280 --> 00:24:42,080
Let's go.

496
00:25:13,360 --> 00:25:14,560
Please, don't kill me!

497
00:25:15,080 --> 00:25:16,520
Don't kill me!

498
00:25:16,800 --> 00:25:17,800
Who are you?

499
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:20,200
Why are you fleeing at this hour?

500
00:25:20,840 --> 00:25:21,960
My name is Xu Jize.

501
00:25:22,440 --> 00:25:24,520
Please, don't kill me!

502
00:25:24,760 --> 00:25:25,560
Over there...

503
00:25:27,920 --> 00:25:30,120
Someone died over there!

504
00:25:31,720 --> 00:25:32,800
Xu Jize?

505
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:35,600
Are you that wedding attendant?

506
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:39,280
Hand him over to Lord Mo.

507
00:25:44,880 --> 00:25:46,480
You are quite something, huh?

508
00:25:46,880 --> 00:25:48,680
Pushed a civilian out to intercept a suspect?

509
00:25:48,920 --> 00:25:50,520
Is this the style of the Imperial Guard?

510
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:52,080
The style of the Imperial Guard?

511
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:54,400
Is it a machine that kills many,

512
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:56,480
or a demon that stops children

513
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:57,280
from crying at night?

514
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:01,400
Which one does

515
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:02,480
Mr. Pan prefer?

516
00:26:09,760 --> 00:26:12,280
Lord Commander, you are quite self-aware.

517
00:26:12,360 --> 00:26:13,520
I admire that.

518
00:26:14,080 --> 00:26:14,600
Really.

519
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:16,960
But since we're at this point,

520
00:26:17,680 --> 00:26:19,080
let's speak frankly.

521
00:26:19,320 --> 00:26:20,880
You constantly target me,

522
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:22,080
always pick on me.

523
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:23,040
If so,

524
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:24,120
why did you insist on dragging me

525
00:26:24,120 --> 00:26:24,920
to pursue the culprit together?

526
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:26,840
Mr. Pan, you are also self-aware.

527
00:26:27,880 --> 00:26:29,240
You know you're in my way.

528
00:26:29,600 --> 00:26:31,120
Why do you keep showing up?

529
00:26:32,040 --> 00:26:33,640
I'm doing this out of necessity

530
00:26:33,840 --> 00:26:34,720
for the sake of solving the case.

531
00:26:35,480 --> 00:26:36,840
Necessity?

532
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:40,680
Showing off even if I was at the scene.

533
00:26:41,480 --> 00:26:42,840
Was that also out of necessity?

534
00:26:56,280 --> 00:26:57,400
[Help!]

535
00:27:00,520 --> 00:27:01,680
Why did it suddenly become quiet?

536
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:35,440
You,

537
00:27:36,760 --> 00:27:37,720
go down there and take a look.

538
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:40,320
Why should I go down?

539
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:42,000
You, an honorable commander

540
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:42,760
are still here.

541
00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:44,280
Who knows what was happening down there?

542
00:27:44,280 --> 00:27:44,920
Besides,

543
00:27:44,920 --> 00:27:45,400
if I go down

544
00:27:45,400 --> 00:27:46,680
and get killed, what then?

545
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,400
If you die,

546
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:51,600
I will collect your body,

547
00:27:51,960 --> 00:27:53,360
build a grave for you,

548
00:27:53,360 --> 00:27:54,400
and ensure your spirit

549
00:27:54,400 --> 00:27:55,440
doesn't wander about,

550
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:56,480
so as not to scare others.

551
00:27:56,480 --> 00:27:57,480
Why are you so sharp-tongued?

552
00:27:57,480 --> 00:27:58,320
You're at a loss for words, aren't you?

553
00:27:59,800 --> 00:28:00,640
Get your arse down there!

554
00:28:03,240 --> 00:28:05,840
I'll assess the situation first.

555
00:28:17,680 --> 00:28:18,480
You are?

556
00:28:19,800 --> 00:28:21,440
Don't be afraid. I'm here to rescue you!

557
00:28:29,480 --> 00:28:30,280
Lord Shen!

558
00:28:52,120 --> 00:28:53,720
You are that bride from today's wedding?

559
00:28:57,080 --> 00:28:57,880
Yes,

560
00:28:58,560 --> 00:28:59,840
I am Du Xiaowan.

561
00:29:00,240 --> 00:29:01,760
Save me, my lord!

562
00:29:04,520 --> 00:29:06,000
There's another person down there,

563
00:29:06,080 --> 00:29:07,040
another one!

564
00:29:13,800 --> 00:29:15,080
At least you have a conscience.

565
00:29:15,640 --> 00:29:16,920
I climbed up on my own.

566
00:29:18,200 --> 00:29:19,000
My back!

567
00:29:22,280 --> 00:29:23,680
You call yourself a commander,

568
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:25,280
yet you have no honor.

569
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:26,840
You keep stabbing me in the back!

570
00:29:27,360 --> 00:29:28,360
I wasn't talking about you.

571
00:29:30,320 --> 00:29:31,240
There's another one.

572
00:29:32,200 --> 00:29:33,320
A dead man!

573
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:54,760
You all,

574
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:56,920
go secure the perimeter.

575
00:29:56,920 --> 00:29:57,640
Jing Lin,

576
00:29:58,160 --> 00:29:58,920
check if there's anything

577
00:29:58,920 --> 00:29:59,880
unusual down there.

578
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:00,600
Understood!

579
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:35,800
Lord Shen,

580
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:37,000
there's nothing unusual down there.

581
