00:40:02,480 --> 00:40:03,280
[as if someone]

870
00:40:03,280 --> 00:40:04,680
[had fallen beside me.]

871
00:40:05,080 --> 00:40:06,200
[The sack loosened,]

872
00:40:06,240 --> 00:40:07,560
[and I managed to crawl out.]

873
00:40:11,000 --> 00:40:12,000
Help!

874
00:40:12,720 --> 00:40:14,240
[I heard someone approaching,]

875
00:40:14,640 --> 00:40:15,440
[but I was afraid it was]

876
00:40:15,440 --> 00:40:17,040
[the accomplice who had fled earlier,]

877
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:19,200
so I stopped calling out.

878
00:40:19,880 --> 00:40:20,640
It wasn't until someone

879
00:40:20,640 --> 00:40:21,720
jumped down the well

880
00:40:21,720 --> 00:40:22,760
that I was finally rescued.

881
00:40:25,680 --> 00:40:27,320
Since you overheard their conversation,

882
00:40:27,640 --> 00:40:29,200
can you identify by his voice

883
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:30,040
if that person

884
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:31,640
was Xu Jize?

885
00:40:35,200 --> 00:40:36,000
The situation was dire,

886
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:37,280
and I was terrified.

887
00:40:37,720 --> 00:40:39,400
I was so scared that my head was spinning,

888
00:40:40,120 --> 00:40:41,880
and I couldn't discern whose voice it was.

889
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:45,720
Lady Du has made it

890
00:40:45,720 --> 00:40:46,680
quite clear.

891
00:40:46,880 --> 00:40:48,600
In her final moments before fainting,

892
00:40:49,120 --> 00:40:50,720
she saw Xu Jize.

893
00:40:51,040 --> 00:40:52,760
Regardless of if you are the murderer,

894
00:40:53,120 --> 00:40:54,040
this case

895
00:40:54,040 --> 00:40:55,840
is undoubtedly connected to you.

896
00:40:55,840 --> 00:40:56,480
I...

897
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:59,160
Xu Jize, you scoundrel!

898
00:40:59,360 --> 00:41:00,400
Bastard!

899
00:41:00,680 --> 00:41:01,520
Animal!

900
00:41:02,160 --> 00:41:02,960
Silence!

901
00:41:03,080 --> 00:41:04,040
What an animal!

902
00:41:04,040 --> 00:41:05,560
You must not act unruly in court!

903
00:41:07,920 --> 00:41:08,720
My lady,

904
00:41:08,720 --> 00:41:09,880
Lord Shen cannot come in person,

905
00:41:09,880 --> 00:41:10,880
so I was sent to present the evidence

906
00:41:10,880 --> 00:41:11,800
to the court.

907
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:15,440
There is evidence,

908
00:41:15,720 --> 00:41:16,720
and there are follow-up actions.

909
00:41:17,240 --> 00:41:18,320
Why didn't you report it sooner?

910
00:41:19,320 --> 00:41:20,640
I'm not your subordinate.

911
00:41:20,720 --> 00:41:22,160
Why should I report everything to you?

912
00:41:24,240 --> 00:41:25,640
No wonder you work under that man;

913
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:27,200
you're truly petty!

914
00:41:27,600 --> 00:41:28,400
Xu Jize,

915
00:41:28,680 --> 00:41:29,760
now that it has come to this,

916
00:41:29,760 --> 00:41:31,120
what else do you have to say?

917
00:41:31,160 --> 00:41:31,920
My lord,

918
00:41:31,920 --> 00:41:33,120
I'm truly wronged!

919
00:41:33,440 --> 00:41:34,480
On the wedding day,

920
00:41:34,520 --> 00:41:36,440
it's common for the bride to go

921
00:41:36,520 --> 00:41:37,280
without food all day

922
00:41:37,280 --> 00:41:38,600
and fall into a deep sleep.

923
00:41:38,960 --> 00:41:40,680
Seeing the bride lacking energy,

924
00:41:40,840 --> 00:41:41,640
I immediately left the room

925
00:41:41,640 --> 00:41:43,080
to avoid any embarrassment.

926
00:41:43,080 --> 00:41:45,720
Then the culprit abducted the bride,

927
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:47,320
and only then did I chase after him!

928
00:41:47,520 --> 00:41:48,560
Stop trying to weasel out of it!

929
00:41:50,040 --> 00:41:51,360
What happened after you chased out?

930
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:52,720
What did you see? Speak!

931
00:41:53,200 --> 00:41:54,920
I'm not sure how far I chased,

932
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:55,800
but then

933
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:57,200
I saw

934
00:41:57,200 --> 00:41:58,480
a shadow with a knife.

935
00:41:58,520 --> 00:41:59,800
The person who abducted Lady Du

936
00:41:59,800 --> 00:42:01,000
was lying nearby.

937
00:42:01,680 --> 00:42:02,920
As a mere scholar,

938
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:04,320
physical strength isn't my forte,

939
00:42:04,440 --> 00:42:06,000
so I dared not confront him.

940
00:42:07,160 --> 00:42:08,400
I turned and ran

941
00:42:08,640 --> 00:42:10,040
until I encountered the guardsmen,

942
00:42:10,040 --> 00:42:11,480
which saved my life.

943
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:22,720
My lady,

944
00:42:23,360 --> 00:42:24,480
what is this for?

945
00:42:24,720 --> 00:42:25,920
Men and women should keep a respectful distance.

946
00:42:27,160 --> 00:42:29,480
Mr. Xu, the embroidery on your clothes

947
00:42:29,600 --> 00:42:31,040
is truly exquisite.

948
00:42:31,360 --> 00:42:33,280
The peach blossom pattern at the collar,

949
00:42:33,720 --> 00:42:35,760
I wonder which fair lady

950
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:36,960
embroidered it for you?

